          "lang": "en",
          "value": "Europe: France Netherlands Germany Switzerland Belgium. Adolescents and their parents in France were recruited from two specialised psychoactive substance addiction centres that offer consultations for young drug users according to the MILDT protocol: Tolbiac Emergency Resource Centre, part of the Institute Mutual Montsouris (Paris, thirteenth municipal district), and the Specialised Drug Addiction Treatment Centre (CSST) and Drug Addiction Support Centre (CEDAT) in Mantes-la-Jolie that are managed by the Mignot Hospital in Versailles."
